SUBENT        A1509001   20260318   20260508   20260508       A133
BIB                  9         16
TITLE      7Li(p,n)7Be neutron polarization measurements for
            Ep=3.0 to 5.5 MeV
AUTHOR     (S.T.Thornton,C.L.Morris,J.R.Smith,R.P.Fogel)
REFERENCE  (J,NP/A,169,131,1971)
INSTITUTE  (1USAVIR)
FACILITY   (VDG,1USAVIR)
SAMPLE     Targets were made by evaporating Li from LiH onto Ta
           backings
METHOD     (TOF)
DETECTOR   (SCIN) Rectangular NE102 plastic scintillators: 15 cm
           high, 5 cm wide and 7.5 cm deep.
HISTORY    (19800813C) Compilation produced by RFNC-VNIIEF Sarov
           (19990323U)CNPD: corrected 4-dig. year and lower cases.
           (20040216A) Change of E-LVL in Sub-002
           (20260318U) SD: Corrections in all Subents.
           Subent 003 added.
ENDBIB              16
